App-Diskd version 0.01
======================

An example POE-based, peer-to-peer disk finder/announcer

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

  POE
  POE::Session
  POE::Wheel::Run
  POE::Wheel::SocketFactory
  POE::Filter::Line
  POE::Wheel::ReadWrite
  POE::Wheel::ReadLine
  Sys::Hostname
  Net::Nslookup
  YAML::XS
  IO::Socket::Multicast
  Socket

DOCUMENTATION

  Before installation, use perldoc ./lib/App/Diskd.pm

  After installation, use perldoc App::Diskd

